### Create product to trigger calculatedPrice background job
# @name CreateProductForBgJobRequest
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [201]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
POST {{ApiBaseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Background-Delay: 1000

{
    "name": "Background Job Test Product",
    "price": 25.00,
    "category": "Testing"
}

###

### Poll product until calculatedPrice is set by background job
# @name PollProductCalculatedPriceRequest
## RETRY-UNTIL-TEST-PASS: calculatedPrice should be set
## RETRY-MAX-ATTEMPTS: 15
## RETRY-BACKOFF-TYPE: Constant
## RETRY-MAX-DELAY: 00:00:01
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}/products/{{CreateProductForBgJobRequest.response.body.$.id}}
Accept: application/json
